text: Belfaux (Dictionnaire-Dikchenéro: Français-Patois/Patê-Franché. Société cantonale des patoisans fribourgeois. Fribourg: 2013. p. 74) is a municipality of the district Saane in the canton of Fribourg in Switzerland. On 1 January 2016, Autafond became the municipality of Belfaux.Nomenklaturen – Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz accessed 3 February 2016 == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Municipalities in Sarine
